分天份三分努力<br />\n大學九分天份一分努力<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同意大學要天份<br />\n但dse要既係努力+運(中文果d)</blockquote><br />\n我就讀緊asso 但睇見啲人<br />\n平時勤力到要係campus訓覺<br />\n但岩岩過3/唔過3<br />\n唔係想笑佢地 但讀到去專一科既野<br />\n就係講緊你岩唔岩果科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n讀Asso識人好過識字。<br />\n<br />\n有source有tips，好過盲公。<br />\n識人dse 333332，gpa3.8，retake考十世都入唔到三大"},{"pid":"a3bb06652a259ef05d9d81a48fc88c8fa0d761a4","tid":135660,"uid":12110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T16:30:06.000Z","msg":"其實好睇天分<br />\n我study leave 日日都拎幾個鐘打lol 8 個鐘溫書都咪照入hku<br />\n我其他科唔勁但就屈人ICT<br />\n而家sem1 讀engine programming 走曬堂都照拎a+<br />\n利申：語文廢j 第時做it 狗"},{"pid":"ed4b0ef0a12efc5d6d79970ecf49cc787d9767cc","tid":135660,"uid":6132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T16:34:18.000Z","msg":"通常班入面一定有一種人好熱衷於學校既野，班會班際社際學生會都好active，同老師關係好好，sba拎好高分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢種人一放榜就會唔知匿左係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b68947930af1fb6d6045342cd354107964356827","tid":135660,"uid":144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T16:37:18.000Z","msg":"DSE其實唔難"},{"pid":"87012f9584670ada746bd478a7f1a164f5195221","tid":135660,"uid":1971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T16:45:04.000Z","msg":"係咪因為識得放鬆自己 個腦會靈活啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9a459bfc662af43eac13af29f3d1503988aa96c","tid":135660,"uid":2467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T16:56:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪因為識得放鬆自己 個腦會靈活啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n溫到一個層次。冇溫勝有溫。"},{"pid":"ce5640e31cfe29c1942751c576683517d462a26e","tid":135660,"uid":83941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T17:00:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33d25489f0e8d97947fb4be3047f8dcfdbbe998d","tid":135660,"uid":33756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T17:01:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個po好多認屎認屁 以為細個俾老師讚有小聰明 自己就真係好撚醒嗰d人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61a9f6c65b19c05e02806e9a5d097600fdf2247e","tid":135660,"uid":19775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T17:04:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>通常班入面一定有一種人好熱衷於學校既野，班會班際社際學生會都好active，同老師關係好好，sba拎好高分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢種人一放榜就會唔知匿左係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n喺咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我身邊又唔喺咁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但其實搞事嘅都喺同一班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ef239712cbcd4057db9c46dd34ee6c360502f97","tid":135660,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T17:06:05.000Z","msg":"入左hku就變哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea1574726a481cfdb8878b3f17f0bae67421e75e","tid":135660,"uid":77740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T17:27:42.000Z","msg":"筆記唔係死抄爛抄就會識，用錯方法就等死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n入大學從來都唔係用乖唔乖黎做標準，乖但蠢都係冇得救，好心樓主唔好再自我安慰話搞事既先入到大學<br />\n<br />\n另外想比下啲意見retaker，由其英文差既，reading同listening有得揀卷作答，如果對自己英文冇信心，我會建議大家做B1，雖然B1會扣分，但最高都有level 4。我用自己做例子，我英文廢，第一年dse英文得2（3322），第二年retake英文改變策略，揀左reading B1，終於升到3（4322），最後入左薄扶林大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  （當然我其他卷高分）"},{"pid":"2ffd84ff6de78acb5e09e1ca55a09238b6942346","tid":135660,"uid":13317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T20:35:56.000Z","msg":"yes<br />\n以前成日唔返學 上堂玩電話唔聽書 又訓覺 唔交功課 特別係中文科同數學科<br />\n不過放左學會好勤力咁溫<br />\n最後hku<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過有啲勁乖既反而入左bu/恆管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}